OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FConservationists are calling for laws
OL,7,Fto be changed so animals such as bison
OL,8,Fand elk can be more easily introduced
OL,9,Fto landscapes to help restore nature.
OL,11,FEuropean bison, the closest living
OL,12,Frelative to ancient steppe bison that
OL,13,Fwould have lived in Britain thousands
OL,14,Fof years ago, already roam in heavily-
OL,15,Ffenced woodland in Kent where their
OL,16,Fbrowsing is beginning to benefit the
OL,17,Fnatural habitat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
