PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FThere are plans to introduce elk ` a
OL,7,Flarge deer species which was hunted to
OL,8,Fextinction in Britain around 2,500 to
OL,9,F3,000 years ago ` into wetland habitat
OL,10,Fin Nottinghamshire alongside beavers,
OL,11,Fwhere it is hoped they will boost the
OL,12,Fecosystem.
OL,14,FBut conservationists behind the
OL,15,Fschemes say they are having to
OL,16,Fnavigate a complicated regime that
OL,17,Ftreats large herbivores such as bison
OL,18,Fand elk as "dangerous wild animals",
OL,19,Fdealt with in the same licensing
OL,20,Fprocedure as lions, tigers or cobras.
OL,26,@zD@LOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
