CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FOne of the rangers working with the
OL,7,Fsmall herd of bison in West Blean and
OL,8,FThornden Woods, Kent, Hannah Mackins,
OL,9,Fsaid a local had described the 6ft
OL,10,Fwild animal fencing with gates and
OL,11,Fbarbed wire as "a bit Jurassic Park",
OL,12,Ffor an animal that is similar to
OL,13,Fcattle.
OL,15,FBut, the bison herd also fall under
OL,16,Ffarming requirements such as ear-
OL,17,Ftagging and bluetongue and bovine TB
OL,18,Ftesting regimes.
OL,26,@sD@POUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
