PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FMs Mackins said "it feels like a
OL,7,Freally hard, big mountain to get over"
OL,8,Fto bring in animals such as bison but
OL,9,Fsuggested it would not always be that
OL,10,Fway, pointing to the continent where
OL,11,Fschemes used to have to put up fencing
OL,12,Faround bison and no longer have to.
OL,14,FThe Wildlife Trusts are calling for a
OL,15,F"Bison and Elk return Bill", among a
OL,16,Fraft of nature-supporting legislation
OL,17,Fthey want to see in this week's Kings
OL,18,FSpeech, to create a new regulatory
OL,19,Fregime for the reintroduction of large
OL,20,Fherbivores to the wild in England.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@fO]wD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
