PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FStan Smith, head of landscape and
OL,7,Fspecies recovery at the Wildlife
OL,8,FTrusts, said the network of charities
OL,9,Fuse large herbivores ` which also
OL,10,Finclude native breeds such as Exmoor
OL,11,Fponies and Highland and longhorn
OL,12,Fcattle ` to manage nature reserves.
OL,14,F"But what we really want to see is a
OL,15,Freal scaling up of the ability to use
OL,16,Flarge herbivores across much larger
OL,17,Flandscape areas," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
