OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,F"If we are really serious about
OL,7,Fdelivering on our national commitments
OL,8,Ffor 30X30 ` that's 30% of land and sea
OL,9,Ffor nature by 2030 ` then we really
OL,10,Fneed to think about how we actually
OL,11,Fmanage large landscape areas and have
OL,12,Fthem function for nature.
OL,14,F"Large herbivores are really the only
OL,15,Fway to do that."
OL,17,FMr Smith said the trusts wanted to see
OL,18,Fa new category created for these
OL,19,Fanimals as "kept wild", with a
OL,20,Fspecific licensing regime for large
OL,21,Fherbivores over large landscape areas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@PO]{D@LOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
