PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FThis would require regular checks and,
OL,7,Fif necessary, intervention to ensure
OL,8,Fanimal welfare, but they would be
OL,9,Fallowed to live out their lives in a
OL,10,Fmuch more natural system.
OL,12,FIn West Blean and Thornden Woods, the
OL,13,Fbison ` which unlike cattle have
OL,14,Fbottom and top teeth, broadening what
OL,15,Fthey can feed on ` are already having
OL,16,Fan impact by disturbing the dense,
OL,17,Fscrubby wood, bringing more light to
OL,18,Fthe forest floor and allowing other
OL,19,Fwoodland plants to grow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
