PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,FThe Wildlife Trusts are also calling
OL,7,Ffor other Bills in the King's Speech
OL,8,Fto support nature, including
OL,9,Flegislation to give the Department for
OL,10,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,11,F(Defra) emergency powers to ban bottom
OL,12,Ftrawling in marine protected areas.
OL,14,FA Defra spokesperson said: "This
OL,15,FGovernment is committed to protecting
OL,16,Fand restoring our most threatened
OL,17,Fnative wildlife to reverse the decline
OL,18,Fof nature and protect it for
OL,19,Fgenerations to come.
OL,26,@vD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
