CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778490376
OL,3,CNew laws needed to help bring in bison
OL,4,Cand elk to boost nature, experts urge
OL,6,F"We are investing #60 million over the
OL,7,Fnext three years into the Species
OL,8,FRecovery Programme, marking the
OL,9,Flargest ever Government investment in
OL,10,Fdirectly supporting threatened
OL,11,Fspecies. We're also returning iconic
OL,12,Fspecies like beavers and golden eagles
OL,13,Fto England once more."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
